This is the same as TeX, except that it accepts only valid UTF-8 input.

Change-files are nimilar to Knuth's changes for SPARC.

Multiple languages may be adopted as explained here: <Olsak's article about xordcode (encTeX v1)>

export MYTEXFONTS=/usr/share/texlive/texmf-dist/fonts/tfm/public/knuth-lib:/usr/share/texlive/texmf-dist/fonts/tfm/public/cm
export MYTEXINPUTS=.:/usr/share/texlive/texmf-dist/tex/plain/base:/usr/share/texlive/texmf-dist/tex/generic/hyphen:/usr/share/texlive/texmf-dist/tex/plain/knuth-lib
export MYTEXPOOL=/home/user/mytex
export MYTEXFORMATS=/home/user/mytex

/home/user/mytex/initex plain # type `\dump'

/home/user/mytex/virtex -format=tex story # type `\end'
